{"tid":591313,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得鄭智係比人嚴重低估","createTime":"2018-03-13T12:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T13:59:38.000Z","uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"411c0ba4fa1bcb737c18f366f24eb8dda3781236","tid":591313,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/195427_689a120783717bb095d04edd3ff054bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F195427_689a120783717bb095d04edd3ff054bc.png&h=ea368d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭智個種區域策應能力真係亞洲一流，佢本身係右後衛出生，但係基本上球場上所有位置都打得，無論係中場、翼鋒、中鋒都能夠勝任，而且係中國少有在歐洲聯賽證明自己的優秀球員，係廣州恆大擔任防守中場，係球隊的攻守轉換點，無疑是恆大多個聯賽冠軍的大功臣，堪稱中國的布斯基斯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攻防集錦:<br />\n<a href=\"https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzI2Njg1ODEwMA==.html?sharefrom=iphone&amp;sharekey=5c57c78e9bbff3f011296340db511b035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fv.youku.com%2Fv_show%2Fid_XMzI2Njg1ODEwMA%3D%3D.html%3Fsharefrom%3Diphone%26sharekey%3D5c57c78e9bbff3f011296340db511b035&d=Lu215eCuhLP2KVPXsKraLp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=933e58cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzI2Njg1ODEwMA==.html?sharefrom=iphone&amp;sharekey=5c57c78e9bbff3f011296340db511b035</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zb5ETn7wj70\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fzb5ETn7wj70&d=Lu215eCuhLP2KVPXsKraLp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7b53bd19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zb5ETn7wj70</a>"},{"pid":"a7ecb360bb97127e7f83e9919e34f4214191b350","tid":591313,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"係咪弱智同茅柴果方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}